snippet.title: Chains of Freedom Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Spring Showcase 2025
snippet.description:
Thanks to a musical number, we learned more about Billie Bust Up's story during the Future Games Show Spring Showcase. This fantastical 3D platformer is coming soon to PC. 

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS #chainsoffreedom

Future Publishing uses the Epidemic Sound Library and Adobe Creative Cloud Generative AI features
